org.eclipse.e4.ui.model.application.ui.menu

Enum ItemType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ItemType>
      • org.eclipse.e4.ui.model.application.ui.menu.ItemType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ItemType>

    public enum ItemType
extends Enum<ItemType>
    A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Item Type', and utility methods for working with them.

    This enum defines the style of a menu or toolbar item.

    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    MenuPackageImpl.getItemType()
